des:
Elvis Presley Facts is a skill to help you to know more about Elvis Presley .


The skill will loop automatically,to pause it just say " Stop"
 
To start the skill just say:

"Alexa,open Elvis Presley facts"
"Alexa, start Elvis Presley facts"
"Alexa, launch Elvis Presley facts"

If you want to make pause or stop just say : "Stop"
if you need help just say : "help"

To activate the skill: Search for the mobile app Alexa or Amazon.com for "Elvis Presley Facts"

On the "Elvis Presley Facts" skill page, click the enable button.
